  "prompt": "Who writes the best class notes in IIT, Bombay?",
  "response": "Determining who writes the \"best\" class notes at IIT Bombay is subjective and varies among students. Different students have their own styles and strengths when it comes to note-taking. Some may focus on clarity, while others might prioritize depth of understanding or thorough organization. Additionally, preferences can vary based on the subject or individual teaching styles of professors. \n\nIf you're looking for high-quality notes, it might be helpful to connect with senior students, check social media groups, or look for study resources shared among your peers. Many students often share their notes within study groups, which can also provide a diverse range of perspectives.",
